cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.DS 

The paper deals with the efficient execution of deep convolutional neural networks (CNN) on edge devices, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The approach presented in the paper involves training CNN models with binary input data, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper evaluates the approach on three datasets, which involves data analysis and processing, making it relevant to data science (cs.DS).
